Would be still good to have a flash message on account creation to encourage people to add personal their Full name. This is similar to &lt;a class="closed ticket" href="http://localhost/ticket/1413" title="enhancement: Ask users to 'add email address' when logged in (closed: fixed)"&gt;#1413&lt;/a&gt; so I'll close this ticket and add it there.
